## Migration Strategy

### Phase 1: Create Generic Endpoints (Completed)
- ✅ `/api/v1/chat/completions` - Already exists
- ✅ `/api/v1/mcp/:provider/:action` - Implemented

### Phase 2: Add Missing Generic Endpoints (In Progress)
- ⏳ `/api/v1/images/generate` - To be implemented
- ⏳ MCP Provider Config - To be created

### Phase 3: Migrate Existing Endpoints (Planned)
- `/api/v1/tavily/search` → `/api/v1/mcp/tavily/search`
- `/api/v1/perplexity/search` → Keep as-is (unique integration)

### Phase 4: Deprecate Old Endpoints (Future)
- Mark old endpoints as `@deprecated`
- Keep for 6 months for backward compatibility
- Add deprecation warnings to responses
- Remove after grace period

